---
const socialLinks = [
  {
    name: "Facebook",
    url: "https://facebook.com/ofmonstersandmen",
    icon: "facebook",
  },
  {
    name: "Instagram",
    url: "https://instagram.com/ofmonstersandmen",
    icon: "instagram",
  },
  {
    name: "YouTube",
    url: "https://youtube.com/ofmonstersandmen",
    icon: "youtube",
  },
];
---

<footer class="bg-stone-800 text-stone-300 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Of Monsters and Men</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-md">
          Una banda islandesa que fusiona el folclore nórdico con sonidos
          contemporáneos, creando música que transporta a paisajes etéreos y
          bosques ancestrales.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          {
            socialLinks.map((link) => (
              <a
                href={link.url}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-stone-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200"
                aria-label={link.name}
              >
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  {link.icon === "facebook" && (
                    <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z" />
